<br>
Changing spells, and coming up with new spells, making sure there are no crashing issues with new spells/songs (ask bards about Katta and proc'ing weapons, we'd have come unglued if everytime we cast a spell our keyboards froze up), making sure the spell does what it's supposed to do, making sure there are no stacking bugs with any other class of spells or with any other series of spells we have, ensuring that the spell doesn't interact with any other spell or mob in a way it wasn't designed to interact...all of that is much much more time consuming.<br>
<br>
I'm guessing the reason we saw mage focus items first is because they are a &quot;simple&quot; summoning spell, and the product of the summoning is like any other item in game, so it was fairly easy to do.<br>
<br>
Heal spells, damage spells, buff spells, these I'm sure will take longer due to their complexity.  We've all seen it before, and many have said &quot;why can't VI get it right before they send it to live servers&quot;.  I would much rather be patient and get spells that work the first time, than have them roll out some half finished product and not be able to use it, or worse, have it possibly crash other things I can currently use. <p>Jinjre Meadowdancer<BR>Dancing in meadows since April 22nd, 1999<BR><BR>Money can't buy you happiness, but it can make you more comfortably miserable.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulalian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lalian</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.data-techniques.net/cwm/otn/other/yleyes.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/18/02 7:46:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27149.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Caster Balance Update</span><hr size=1> Don't mention Katta.  SHEESH!  Nice to be able to use it though since the last patch and it came out when? <p><Font Size = 1>
